Magpie
```json
{
  "application": "Magpie",
  "software": [
    {
      "name": "Java",
      "version": "1.8.0",
      "path": "/usr/lib/jvm/jre-1.8.0/"
    },
    {
      "name": "Python",
      "version": "Not Specified",
      "path": "/usr/bin/python"
    },
    {
      "name": "Spark",
      "version": "3.0.3-bin-hadoop3.2",
      "path": "${HOME}/spark-${SPARK_VERSION}"
    }
  ],
  "resource_requirements": {
    "node_count": "<my_node_count>",
    "time_limit": "<my_time_in_hours:minutes>",
    "queue": "<my_queue>",
    "job_name": "<my_job_name>",
    "spark_worker_cores_per_node": "8 (estimated if not specified)",
    "spark_worker_memory_per_node": "16000M (estimated if not specified)",
    "spark_job_memory": "2048M (defaults to SPARK_WORKER_MEMORY_PER_NODE)",
    "spark_driver_memory": "2048M (defaults to SPARK_JOB_MEMORY if not specified)",
    "spark_daemon_heap_max": "2000M (defaults to 1000M if not specified)",
    "spark_local_scratch_dir": "/lustre/${USER}/sparkscratch/",
    "spark_default_parallelism": "8 (defaults to number of compute nodes if not specified)"
  },
  "configurations": {
    "magpie_scripts_home": "${HOME}/magpie",
    "magpie_local_dir": "/tmp/${USER}/magpie",
    "magpie_job_type": "spark",
    "magpie_one_time_run": "No (defaults to No)",
    "magpie_pre_job_run": "Not Specified",
    "magpie_post_job_run": "Not Specified",
    "magpie_pre_execute_run": "Not Specified",
    "magpie_post_execute_run": "Not Specified",
    "magpie_environment_variable_script": "Not Specified",
    "magpie_environment_variable_script_shell": "/bin/bash (defaults to $SHELL)",
    "magpie_remote_cmd": "ssh (defaults to ssh)",
    "magpie_remote_cmd_opts": ""
  },
  "other": {
    "mpirun_options": "-genvall -genv MV2_USE_APM 0"
  }
}
```
